Original Text: \f[16]ユイの献身で戦力が\cself[40]回復した！
Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[15]\-[2]Yui's devotion restored \cself[40] points of our fighting strength!

Original Text: \f[16]「あなたはここで一緒にあたしと死ぬの。」
Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[15]\-[2]"You're going to die here with me"

Original Text: \f[16]「だいじょうぶ、痛いのは一瞬だから…。」
Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[15]\-[2]"It's okay, the pain will only last for a moment..."
